The following events will be triggered by the application when dealing with artifacts

* @NewInstance\[klass, type, instance\]@ - when a new artifact is created.
* @LoadAddonsStart\[app\]@ - before any [addons|guide:addons] are initialized.
* @LoadAddonsEnd\[app, addons\]@ - after all [addons|guide:addons] have been initialized. @addons@ is a Map of <name, instance> pairs.
* @LoadAddonStart\[name, addon, app\]@ - before an addon is initialized.
* @LoadAddonEnd\[name, addon, app\]@ - after an addon has been initialized.
